reviewText: Great set of movies.  I highly recommend them for open minded individuals.  Not for the faint at heart.  They are quite comical.

THE SEX PISTOLS ARE THE WORST OF THEM I SUPPOSE.
SOMEBODY SHOULD DIG AND EXCEEDINGLY DEEP WHOLE
This product is for movie connoisseurs who enjoy collecting older movies.  Received promptly and as described. I would recommend this set .
Fantastic as are all of Russ Meyer's films.  Excellent to view these early efforts and the develepment of his unique and wonderful film edditing style.

The only problem was 2 of the four disc were scratched, the product was new, sealed and the shrink wrapped packaging used for mailing was very good. However and I have had this happen when I have special ordered DVD through video stores, the discs during mailing pop out of the holder inside the plastic dvd box and bounce around. I would rather have the new product opened up tape placed to hold the DVD in place or paper DVD sleeves used to stop the scratches from happening. Paying $70.00 + for damaged products is not to great.
